  arm/arm64: Remove unnecessary ISB when doing dcache maintenance
  lib: arm64: Consolidate register definitions to sysreg.h
  arm64: Configure SCTLR_EL1 at boot
  arm64: Disable TTBR1_EL1 translation table walks

